title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Top 5 busiest airports - UK
description:
In this video we will look at the top 5 busiest airports in the UK. We will look both at the default airport scenery but also will review several community addons which are available for some of the airports. During our visit we also spot some cool airplanes which are not even released for MSFS like the A380.

If you want to try the addons yourself download them via the links below:

London Gatwick:
https://flightsim.to/file/5784/gatwick-egkk-ultra-star-edition-phase-1-0

London Stansted:
https://flightsim.to/file/18965/london-stansted-airport-egss

Manchester Airport: night improvement:
https://flightsim.to/file/2460/egcc-manchester-airport-night-lighting-improvement
